    ('Eric Friedman','Freedom from Hunger Fund',28000,NULL,'2008-01-01','year','date of donation announced in announcement',NULL,'http://blog.givewell.org/2011/06/21/guest-post-from-eric-friedman/','Historical donation mentioned when explaining more recent donation. Relevant quote: In early 2007, my life took a turn for the better: I met the woman who is now my wife. In 2008, Freedom from Hunger offered us the opportunity to join them (at our expense) on a site visit to some of their programs in Ghana. During our time there, we spent a significant amount of time with some of their senior staff (including the CEO), three board members, program staff, and their clients. We saw the programs in action, which increased our conviction in what they do.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
